character_name: Brian O'Conner:An LAPD officer sent to infiltrate a crew of hijackers. Mia's love interest.

Dominic Toretto:Leader of the heist crew and a professional street racer. He was banned from professional racing after a violent retaliatory attack on the man who accidentally killed Dominic's father.
Letty Ortiz: A member of Dominic's crew and his girlfriend.
Mia Toretto: Dominic's sister and owner of the Toretto general store. Brian's love interest.
Johnny Tran: A Vietnamese gang leader and rival of Dominic.
Jesse: A member of Dominic's crew. Highly intelligent with math
Leon: A member of Dominic's crew
Vince: A member of Dominic's crew and his childhood friend. He harbors an unrequited love for Mia.
